

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Your Brand</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .hero-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #232f3e;
        }
        .content-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .content-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #232f3e;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        .values-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .value-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .value-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #232f3e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Your Brand</h1>
            <p class="lead">We are committed to delivering exceptional value and innovation to our customers worldwide.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                At Your Brand, our mission is to be the most customer-centric company, where people can find and discover anything they want to buy online. 
                We strive to offer the best selection, prices, and convenience, making life easier for our customers.
            </p>

            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>
                Founded in [Year], Your Brand started with a vision to revolutionize [industry/sector]. Today, we are a global leader, 
                serving millions of customers across [regions/countries]. Our team is driven by a passion for innovation, quality, and impact.
            </p>

            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-item">
                    <h3>Customer Obsession</h3>
                    <p>We start with the customer and work backward, ensuring every decision prioritizes their needs and trust.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-item">
                    <h3>Innovation</h3>
                    <p>We embrace bold ideas and cutting-edge technology to create solutions that transform lives.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-item">
                    <h3>Integrity</h3>
                    <p>We operate with transparency and accountability, building trust with every interaction.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-item">
                    <h3>Excellence</h3>
                    <p>We pursue the highest standards in everything we do, from products to customer service.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Our Impact</h2>
            <p>
                With a presence in [number] countries and a team of [number] dedicated professionals, we’ve empowered 
                [specific achievements, e.g., “millions of customers with fast delivery”]. We’re proud to support 
                [causes, e.g., sustainability, education] and make a positive difference in the world.
            </p>

            <h2>Join Us</h2>
            <p>
                Ready to explore what we offer? Shop our products, connect with our team, or learn more about our journey.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


